flowchart TD
    A[命令: train] --> B[Program.Train]
    B --> C[GenerateAll]
    C --> D[构造 Vocabulary]
    D --> E[构造 TransformerModel]
    E --> F[epoch 循环]
    F --> G[DataGenerator.Batches<br/>添加 SOS/EOS/PAD]
    G --> H[Training.TrainStepBackprop<br/>Forward + Loss + Backward + SGD]
    H --> I[遍历所有 batch]
    I --> J[Training.Validate<br/>验证集 loss]
    J --> F
    F --> K[Evaluation.EvaluateOnValidation<br/>loss/TokenAcc/SeqAcc]
    K --> L[保存模型 SavedModel]

    %% 推理
    M[命令: infer] --> N[Program.RunInfer]
    N --> O[InferenceExample.Run]
    O --> P[TransformerModel.LoadFromDirectory]
    P --> Q[构造示例输入序列]
    Q --> R[DataGenerator.Preprocess]
    R --> S[model.Forward]
    S --> T[Argmax 取预测 token]
    T --> U[vocab.DecodeToDigit]
    U --> V[打印 输入 / 期望 / 预测]